<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content">
<ab><expan>L<ex>ieber</ex></expan> Steffan, uns <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan>
                        fürgelegt Mertein Haller, Karl Holczschuher und
                            <expan>Albr<ex>echt</ex></expan>
<expan>Ebn<ex>er</ex></expan>, <add><expan>uns<ex>er</ex></expan> lieb
                            burger</add>, vormunde frawn Kathrein der Berhtold Hallerin,
                                <expan>uns<ex>er</ex></expan> burgerin,
                            <expan>selige<ex>n</ex></expan> gescheffts, von
                            <expan>derselb<ex>e</ex>n</expan> vormundschaft
                            <expan>wege<ex>n</ex></expan>, wie daz der Kurcz von Onlspach und Hans
                        Künlein von Aychembach dem <expan>Heincze<ex>n</ex></expan> Swarczen von
                        Wustendorff, der <expan>eg<ex>enanten</ex></expan> Hallerin
                                <expan>selige<ex>n</ex></expan>
<expan>armman<ex>n</ex></expan>, mit gewalt on recht czu Aychembach drew
                        pferd und <expan>eine<ex>n</ex></expan> wagen mit
                            <expan>ir<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>czugehöru<ex>n</ex>g</expan>
<expan>genome<ex>n</ex></expan>
<expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan>. <expan>Ro<ex>gamus</ex></expan>, daz ir sie
                        daran weisen wöllet, daz sie dem <expan>egen<ex>anten</ex></expan>
<add>Heinczen Swarczen</add>
<expan>dieselb<ex>e</ex>n</expan> seine pferde und
                            <expan>wage<ex>n</ex></expan> mit <expan>ir<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>czugehöru<ex>n</ex>g</expan>
<expan>widergeb<ex>e</ex>n</expan> und volgen lassen. Das
                                <expan>wölle<ex>n</ex></expan> etc. Und
                            <expan>hete<ex>n</ex></expan> sie <expan>dan<ex>n</ex></expan> czu
                                <expan>demselb<ex>e</ex>n</expan>
<expan>Swarcze<ex>n</ex></expan> icht <expan>czusprech<ex>e</ex>n</expan>,
                                <expan>dar<ex>umb</ex></expan>
<expan>wölle<ex>n</ex></expan> in die <expan>vorgen<ex>anten</ex></expan>
                        vormunde von im <expan>unv<ex>er</ex>czogens</expan> slewnigs
                                <expan>rehte<ex>n</ex></expan>
<expan>g<ex>er</ex>n</expan> helffen, <expan>wen<ex>n</ex></expan> sie des
                                <expan>erma<ex>n</ex>t</expan>
<expan>werde<ex>n</ex></expan>; <expan>ew<ex>r</ex></expan>
<expan>fr<ex>euntlich</ex></expan>
<expan>v<ex>er</ex>schr<ex>iben</ex></expan>
<expan>antw<ex>ur</ex>t</expan> lat uns darümb wider wissen.
                                <expan>Dat<ex>um</ex></expan>
<expan>sabb<ex>a</ex>to</expan>
<expan>p<ex>ost</ex></expan> Erhardi.</ab>
</div>
